<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
OK, class reports have been called for again. With the current situation, this may not be as full featured a report as usual. I am still going to point out obvious problems, and explain obvious deficiencies with the class. I want to narrow it down to the top 3 or 4 things that MUST change for this class to make us viable as the prime CCer of our realm.<P>Now as we have seen, our adaptability has kicked us in the ass again. Everyone respecced to body, got in a decent group, and played wizzy for a week. They earned more RPs than we can as a prime CC character, and those RP totals were tallied. So now those classes that can and do earn reliable RPs are not first priority for attention.<P>The idea is, players want a character they can rely on being the same 2 months down the line. They are concerned that people do not want so much drastic change. and i agree. but i think they are failing to see some characters need immediate drastic change. HOW those RPs were earned were not a factor, only that a certain class can earn them.<P>So the adaptability of the sorceror may have juste hurt ourselves again. So we Can earn RPs as a secondary DD class, and now we may have to. We can NOT provide the primary CC our realm needs on a reliable basis, and it will be a few weeks before this shows itself to be true. We may come up for review if the realm as a whole takes a severe hit since there are going to be so few dedicated mind Sorcs running around now.<P>But a report is due.... Time will hvae to make all this apparent, and all i can do at this point is report it. So here is what i want from anyone who is interested...<P>Keep this thread focused. No debates. One post per person, as if you wrote it in a vaccuum. Do not reference other peoples posts, do not quote others, and keep it clean. I want to copy a 2 or 3 line quote from each of you about the Sorceror and put it into the report.<P>So again, in this thread, 2 or 3 lines about the sorceror. No other real rules, open forum. but keep it to 2 or 3 i can copy and paste directly into the report...<P>And to facilitate this, here is the format.<P>YOUR NAME (YOUR CHARACTER NAME (Level if you like) :&lt;your 3 lines here&gt;<P>So keep it focused and keep it to one post each, not referencing any others since they may not be in the same order when they hit the report. i will start another thread for discussion.<P>Here is an example...<P>I3ullseye (Pointdexter (lev 5 Sorc, Guinevere) :I think Sorcerors are nifty keen neato. Summoning pets and nearsighting the enemy makes us great. Oh wait thats cabbies, thats right sorcerors suck...<P>Hehe, ok, not comments like that, but thats the format to follow.<P>one each...<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
