Hidien (Hidien 50th Scorc Palomides)<P>With the recent changes to mez - reduced efectivness of the area, 1min timer, resist rates, etc.. not to mention the reduced effectivness of a charmed mob, our primary spec ability has taken a major hit. I signed up to do CC for the realm on day one. Since that time I have seen that role diminish to the point of being near useless in RvR. With all the recent changes, there is almost no reason to spec Mind for RvR. This adds to the near uselessnes of Matter for RvR. These changes turn us into "mini" wizards and if I had wanted to be that, I would have played a wizard from the start.
