Natalya Nightwind, lvl 50 Sorceress, Guinevere:<BR>My problem is in the viability of all spec lines.  Body is doing quite well, with a combination of DD and Crowd Control.  Matter needs a little help in the form of increased crowd control (or make the range of the DD/Snare 1500 like all others).  The recent decreases to mez make most sorcerers /respec out of the Mind line completely.  It is also the only class-defining spec line (I think) that grants no bonuses when taken above level 44.  Debuffs should be reworked to be more effective, mind and maybe matter should be tweaked, and support classes should receive realm points for their work.
</FONT>
