Pwylw [lvl38 Matter/Mind sorc Mordred/ lvl31 Matter sorc Andred]<P>Short version as asked: Matter line is awesome, Body line is fine (fix the first spec root problem). We need something insta in the Mind line...<P>Longer version:<BR>Personally I don't see many problems with sorcerer class. I never tried the body line so I will not comment on it (even though it's seems nice if I look around when I play). Myself, I am a matter sorcerer. Since the DoT patch (stacking and scalling with skill), I can finally say that the Matter line is a damn fine line to follow. About the Mind line, we really need something. I don't know what, but I don't see why Hibernia and Midgard got all these instants while we have none. If you check carefully, you will see that, talking about instants, Hibernia as 2 (Champion/Bard) and Midgard as 4 (Healer, Shaman, Skald, Thane). Doing damage of mezzing/stunning, instant casts are insanely powerful when you are dealing with casters since it forces the casters to quick cast while you may not even be in melee range, or to interrupt you, long enough to be in melee range. So we need something insta cast. Root or Mezz would be good, or maybe something like a "Mind shriek", an insta shout with some decent enough damage, maybe snaring or stunning for a very little while.<P>With my matter sorc, I can kill about anyone even con (including skalds if lucky). I consider the sorcerer class done, or close to it.<P>ps: keep in mind that I am not considering myself as a CCer. But nobody said that Sorcerers HAD to be CCers.<P>--------------------<P><B>Pwylw</B><BR>Matter Sorcerer<BR><I>"He who Dots better buy new boots"</I>
