Maltorefas - Merlin - 500k+ RPs - 45 body 24 mind 17 matter<BR>Personally I am happy with my sorc, the combination of nukes, mes, speed, and a pet make it a killer solo/small group class able to take on great odds.  My only gripe is the recent changes to mes time, and the 24 mes not being 350 range, which might get me to respec to 34 mind/41 body.  Other then that I am perfectly happy.  <P>Regarding interuptions... I think it IS a bit overboard but every caster has to deal with it and we do have quickcast... although this TICK TICK TICK thing really annoys me, ie. dead guy interupting me. HAHAH!<P>--------------------<P>Maltorefas, 50 Sorcerer, Merlin
